snippet.title: Devil Mail - Official Trailer | Made with Fancade
snippet.description:
Try this short Voxel-style adventure and explore a small part of the autumn kingdom, where you must find a way to access the castle and deliver an important message to the king, a message from a very far away place...

- Play it on Fancade:
https://play.fancade.com/652FF35AE208BF6D?max_w=2800&max_h=2800

- Available on Itchio:
https://leoescamend.itch.io/devil-mail

(It is recommended to play directly from the fancade application, for mobile devices)

- Download Fancade.
       - App Store:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/fancade/id1280404080

       - Play Store:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.martinmagni.fancade

- Trailer Music.
Comedic Juggernaut - Music to Delight de Kevin MacLeod tiene una licencia Atribución 4.0 de Creative Commons. https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

Fuente: http://incompetech.com/music/royalty-free/index.html?isrc=USUAN1100288

Artista: http://incompetech.com/
